dct_description_sm: This line data layer represents road centerlines for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2012. The dataset was originally published by the Dane County Land Information Office in 2012.[This layer is a detailed line coverage of the Dane County roadway network containing attributes such as street name and address ranges, ZIP codes, speed limits and routing.]
